description: The beautiful chain is the world's first medical and industrial chain, which allows medical and aesthetic institutions, practitioners' qualifications and consumer body data to be chained and become value nodes. Its token HEY is a pass for the medical and industrial chain. In addition to opening up the data of all aspects of the medical and aesthetic industry, it will also promote value circulation through the medical and aesthetic HIS system, medical beauty live Dapp, game mining and other means. In the end, HEY will become an asset token and support consumption in physical stores
name: HealthBeautyChain
